methods.name: int getSavepointId() throws SQLException
methods.comment: * Retrieves the generated ID for the savepoint that this * Savepoint object represents. * @return the numeric ID of this savepoint * @exception SQLException if this is a named savepoint * @since 1.4

methods.name: String getSavepointName() throws SQLException
methods.comment: * Retrieves the name of the savepoint that this Savepoint * object represents. * @return the name of this savepoint * @exception SQLException if this is an un-named savepoint * @since 1.4
